    return ( <

        Row >
        <
        Col > 1 of 1 < /Col> <
        Col > < ul className = "navbarList" >

        li >

        /li> <
        li >
        <

        className = "navbarListAnchor" > Logout < /Link> <

        /Row> <
        /Container>

}

export default Header;
